&bull; Implement code image signing and verification techniques<br />
&bull; Implement interfaces to hardware security mechanisms embedded in media SOCs<br />
&bull; Provide tier 3 technical support as needed<br />
&bull; Others as assigned</p>
<p>
This position reports to a technical manager within the engineering team.</p>
<p>
<br />
