&bull; Significant experience in:&nbsp;<br />
o Low-level programming (boot loader, coding on hardware or on top of driver level)<br />
o Cryptology (ciphers, signing processes, certificates, etc.)<br />
o Secure hardware coding and configuration<br />
&bull; Linux experience from bootloader to kernel to drivers to application programming<br />
